This annual review is a summary of our global impact for children, particularly girls, in 2021. Plan International strives for a just world that advances children’s rights and equality for girls. In this report, you'll find out how we are working towards delivering greater impact for vulnerable and excluded children, especially girls, influencing greater change at local and global levels and transforming girls' lives. Click on download below to read our annual review in English, French or Spanish, as well as our combined financial statements. A review of the global challenges and the achievements in Plan International’s programming and influencing work in 2021. By Raj Nooyi, Interim CEO and Gunvor Kronman, Chair, Plan International.